ds]]''\n| [[Jennifer Yuh Nelson]]\n| [[20th Century Fox]]<br />[[21 Laps Entertainment]]\n| Orchestra conducted by [[Timothy Williams]] & Benjamin Wallfisch\n|-\n! ''[[King of Thieves (2018 film)|King of Thieves]]''\n| [[James Marsh (director)|James Marsh]]\n| [[Working Title Films]]<br />[[StudioCanal UK]]\n| Orchestra Conducted by Chris Egan\n|-\n! ''[[The Vanishing (2018 film)|The Vanishing]]''\n| Kristoffer Nyholm\n| [[Cross Creek Pictures]]<br />[[Saban Entertainment]]<br />[[Lionsgate Films]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2019\n! ''[[Serenity (2019 film)|Serenity]]''\n| [[Steven Knight]]\n| [[IM Global]]\n| Additional music by Antonio Andrade, orchestra conducted by Geoff Alexander\n|-\n! ''[[Shazam! (film)|Shazam!]]''\n| [[David F. Sandberg]]\n| [[DC Entertainment]]<br />[[New Line Cinema]]<br />[[Warner Bros.|Warner Bros. Pictures]]<br />[[The Safran Company]]\n| Third collaboration with [[David F. Sandberg]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2018/07/21/benjamin-wallfisch-to-score-david-f-sandbergs-shazam/|title=Benjamin Wallfisch to Score David F. Sandberg\u2019s \u2018Shazam!\u2019 {{!}} Film Music Reporter|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref> Orchestra Conducted by Chris Egan & Benjamin Wallfisch\n|-\n! ''[[Hellboy (2019 film)|Hellboy]]''\n| [[Neil Marshall]]\n| [[Alchemy (company)|Millennium Films]]<br />[[Dark Horse Entertainment]]\n| Additional music by Antonio Andrade, Jared Fly & Alex Lu. Orchestra conducted by Chris Egan and performed by The Chamber Orchestra of London.\n|-\n! ''[[It Chapter Two]]''\n| [[Andy Muschietti]] \n| [[New Line Cinema]]<br />[[Warner Bros. Pictures]]<br />[[Vertigo Entertainment]]\n| Second collaboration with [[Andy Muschietti]]\n|-\n| 2020\n! ''[[The Invisible Man (2020 film)|The Invisible Man]]''\n| [[Leigh Whannell]]\n| [[Universal Pictures]]<br />[[Blumhouse Productions|Blumhouse]]\n| Orchestra conducted by Chris Egan, performed by The Chamber Orchestra of London\n|-\n| 2021\n! ''[[Mortal Kom